title: Fix
message:
Fix
" E/dalvikvm(776): JNI ERROR (app bug): accessed stale local reference 0x1d500011 (index 4 in a table of size 4)" on 4.x

limit use of DROIDZEBRA_JNI_SETUP. s_env/s_thiz are only valid wihtout the realm of outer JNI call and are only useful for callback function. setters/getters should not call it.

ref:
"JNI Local Reference Changes in ICS"
http://android-developers.blogspot.com/2011/11/jni-local-reference-changes-in-ics.html
